spec_data.Name: perl-DateTime-Format-ICal
spec_data.Description:
This module understands the ICal date/time and duration formats, as defined
in RFC 2445. It can be used to parse these formats in order to create the
appropriate objects.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:47:08 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Parse and format iCal datetime and duration strings
